Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Am I forsaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:13.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}And yet, I keep walking in silence
