Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Cannot escape from tragic fate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:22.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}何度問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:37.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}導く声未だなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:40.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}何度傷つけあえば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:44.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}確かなものを掴めるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}終わりのない理想論
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:48.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}無秩序なノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}不条理な運命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}向き合っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}汚れてしまっていても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}全てに背こうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:58.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Looking for a ray of light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:03.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Find the way by your own
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}孤独の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:10.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Leave it all behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:15.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}最果ての先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:17.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Am I forsaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:21.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}And yet, I keep walking in silence
